This i my best part as we now get to work. With clear requirements in hand i am eager to materialize your idea into its tangible equivalent. Strategy Quality Assuarance. In this phase i present you with the final product over coffee. We test the functionality of the system with some of your users and determine wheather it addresses their needs.
